<node CREATED="1269030055086" ID="Freemind_Link_1010644802" MODIFIED="1269030108870" TEXT="This is created much like a new EnergyPlus Zone,&#xa;however everything in this is interpreted by&#xa;EnergyPlus as ashading surface."/>
